{"tid":1227280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱太古廣場個位烈士 無必要可憐佢 無必要戥佢慘 覺得佢唔值得死","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T16:33:48.000Z","uid":171139,"like":2159,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"394e42f6591a6d4ea89c426147ad8430a9e1d331","tid":1227280,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:48:12.000Z","msg":"佢選擇咗犧牲自己嘅性命去控訴呢個垃圾政府，<br />\n佢早就有呢一切嘅覺悟，<br />\n如果你可憐佢，戥佢慘，覺得佢唔應該死，<br />\n只會係侮辱佢企出天台嘅勇氣！<br />\n<br />\n我哋要同佢講嘅，只有一句話：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Respect! And rest in peace!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢刻，啲警犬一定係以事不關己嘅心態話：呢個人抵死啦！佢自己企出天台，自己攞嚟嘅！<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係覺得佢唔值得為咗呢個政府死，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就講大家令到佢嘅死變得有價值！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日6.16，再一次行出嚟<br />\n為香港人，為香港嘅未來，為所有被捕以及受傷嘅所有義士，<br />\n同埋為呢位為香港奉獻自己性命嘅烈士，<br />\n再一次，再一次奮鬥！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a25d145b2581f32bbf1f08134b8e4fd770bc8137","tid":1227280,"uid":171139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe683f705f93612bcf96e45d0dede1f1fedd8ba4","tid":1227280,"uid":171139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f894156a636cbbad5d21ce5a73a01d7625a49d","tid":1227280,"uid":227267,"like":198,"dislike":1,"score":197,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:50:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭月娥血債血償</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c7f243b6249957723f87bbfad43c35cce27ff957","tid":1227280,"uid":141879,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"聽日遊行要默哀"},{"pid":"68726f076efbfa0fa14ccec3028001dadedcec46","tid":1227280,"uid":258072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以比佢白白犧牲"},{"pid":"9726a0bcdaae5b9315b891851e9dc0b44fd5e89a","tid":1227280,"uid":41292,"like":236,"dislike":0,"score":236,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:54:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄭</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">月</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">娥</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兇</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"f91bc31863d79c3089588bc57f95b47a1942f2e3","tid":1227280,"uid":182822,"like":184,"dislike":0,"score":184,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"唔好再走啦聽日 <br />\n香港人 醒未啊 有人已經死咗啦<br />\n係死咗啊<br />\n佢係同你我一樣每時每刻呼吸住嘅人<br />\n但佢嘅呼吸已經唔再存在<br />\n或者聽日什麼什麼父親節<br />\n或者後日什麼返工返學<br />\n你真係可以繼續無動於衷打個卡影張相就繼續生活落去？<br />\n我已經唔再粗體紅字<br />\n我唔知自己打緊啲咩<br />\n唔好走啦好唔好啊香港人<br />\n唔好再講咩留守係冇意義<br />\n咁難道人地嘅死都係冇意義？<br />\n你唔做我唔做 邊個做？"},{"pid":"6525ed0965ed1e6e5771348034d439fe9ba570a8","tid":1227280,"uid":90166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"No!佢唔係自己跌"},{"pid":"ff7ff8771cc4bbd4e8f616116ea272b263b4b756","tid":1227280,"uid":186,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「黑警冷血，林鄭殺港」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d7874f2843b118e2da4f70447b54a5e7264888bf","tid":1227280,"uid":126054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e2de33b3ebc2a0d818d8d7db36196c7528a49e","tid":1227280,"uid":261180,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Z49uvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Z49uvR.png&h=43abcfc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac7ae4dd2e35d12fd0bfe4ff5950aa94aa532eac","tid":1227280,"uid":36065,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"來生唔好再做香港人"},{"pid":"856955e64693f3a6fed13148565880f5b503e404","tid":1227280,"uid":36970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6525ed0965ed1e6e5771348034d439fe9ba570a8","tid":1227280,"uid":90166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"No!佢唔係自己跌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"竟然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32be3784dd209fca40313945e59a3e076f17c084","tid":1227280,"uid":54995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccc626bf0bfcfa4c4959cfecdf3b4b2f3bd0de5","tid":1227280,"uid":171139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係香港人嘅，聽日同我出嚟！</span></span>"},{"pid":"be6eca4c5b9b133e1c484619e84fef48c11ad49a","tid":1227280,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20229025bd77b48237d0309aa68b8a98244d4f7","tid":1227280,"uid":262187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:05:03.000Z","msg":"真正為香港民主獻出生命既烈士.<br />\nR.I.P<br />\n<br />\n我唔會令你既死白費"},{"pid":"82224d57d0df08a2289d9e938e475300daf90e54","tid":1227280,"uid":171139,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"6525ed0965ed1e6e5771348034d439fe9ba570a8","tid":1227280,"uid":90166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"No!佢唔係自己跌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:06:41.000Z","msg":"事實話就係咁，但佢企得天台，其實都有返咁上下覺悟<br />\n無將自己性命置諸度外嘅人，又點敢企喺隨時會無命嘅地方？"},{"pid":"5adf88d3530edafebee8d3368c6643dd36208971","tid":1227280,"uid":104500,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n佢已經選擇左呢條路<br />\n我地或者會痛哭，或者會憤怒<br />\n但我地要做嘅，<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔係惋惜或嗟嘆</span><br />\n係要尊重佢嘅意志，係要傳承佢嘅信念，係要將佢未酬之壯志一一實現！<br />\n佢見唔到嘅風景，佢見唔到嘅未來，佢見唔到嘅惡有惡報，由我地去見！<br />\n佢實現唔到嘅願望，佢實現唔到嘅目標，佢實現唔到嘅一切一切，都由我地去完成！<br />\n佢係烈士，佢係英雄，佢係以死亡向全香港所有人進諫嘅勇者！麻煩尊重佢嘅選擇同犧牲！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再講多次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個6月16唔上街嘅，邊個都對佢唔住！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個6月16唔上街嘅，邊個都係契弟！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兄弟，一路好走，你嘅犧牲唔會白費，請在朵朵瑰麗雲彩上，看著全港有多少人受你感召，在星期日集結在維園<br />\n我相信、我相信，星期日那聲聲的「反送中」，定必如雷灌耳，聲勢之大，你在天堂也定必聽到。"},{"pid":"05c7ab440056c5f23a627da6fb9fb68bb8e5025b","tid":1227280,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17f0a4133392408180468e556f7a723769feaa8","tid":1227280,"uid":171139,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"唔好話佢慘，呢位烈士佢唔想要人可憐佢<br />\n佢只想要兩件事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>推倒惡法，同埋釋放所有義士同學生！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f23d47a0ef2d884e00e9d0fe7a522e30ad0487b1","tid":1227280,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfb9f75f107d71e2e8d19a6aa79bf5d5d8574de","tid":1227280,"uid":188907,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:13:40.000Z","msg":"唔好鼓吹自殺風氣唔該<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9uERMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9uERMC.png&h=5f21c210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂爭議越演越烈，周日及周三的反修例示威均演變警民衝突。災後心理輔導協會設立「救心熱線」，為受事件影響、對社會死心的市民提供心理支援服務，熱線為51815501。"},{"pid":"a74ba9755502ffb5f936822ee48014ad8585a3a6","tid":1227280,"uid":31423,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"雖然唔想見到，就既然選擇左，只可以尊重，感激，繼承遺志<br />\n&quot;可惜&quot;, &quot;傻&quot; 呢D 說話其實好難聽。。"},{"pid":"e1fa37290e2a24cdb1ee6c9c1a925169c3d8a73f","tid":1227280,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:15:53.000Z","msg":"岩呀 巴打點解要咁傻<img src=\"/assets/fa